---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main>
		<header>
			<h1>⚽ The World of Soccer</h1>
			<p>The beautiful game loved by billions around the globe.</p>
			<p class="page-links">
				<a href="/about">Go to About Page</a>
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="about">
			<h2>About Soccer</h2>
			<p>
				Soccer, known as football outside of North America, is the world's most popular sport.
				Played by over 250 million players in more than 200 countries, it is a game of skill,
				teamwork, and passion. Two teams of eleven players compete to score goals by getting
				the ball into the opposing team's net.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="positions">
			<h2>Player Positions</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Goalkeeper</strong> – Defends the goal and is the only player allowed to use their hands.</li>
				<li><strong>Defender</strong> – Protects the team's goal and stops opposing attackers.</li>
				<li><strong>Midfielder</strong> – Links defense and attack, controlling the pace of the game.</li>
				<li><strong>Forward</strong> – Leads the attack and is primarily responsible for scoring goals.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="tournaments">
			<h2>Major Tournaments</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>FIFA World Cup</strong> – Held every four years, it is the most-watched sporting event in the world.</li>
				<li><strong>UEFA Champions League</strong> – Annual club competition featuring Europe's top teams.</li>
				<li><strong>Copa América</strong> – South America's premier international tournament.</li>
				<li><strong>UEFA European Championship</strong> – Features the top national teams from Europe.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="legends">
			<h2>Soccer Legends</h2>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Pelé</strong> – Brazilian icon and three-time World Cup winner.</li>
				<li><strong>Diego Maradona</strong> – Argentine legend famous for his 1986 World Cup performances.</li>
				<li><strong>Lionel Messi</strong> – Eight-time Ballon d'Or winner and 2022 World Cup champion.</li>
				<li><strong>Cristiano Ronaldo</strong> – Record-breaking scorer and five-time Champions League winner.</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		max-width: 860px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		font-family: Georgia, serif;
		color: #222;
	}

	header {
		text-align: center;
		background-color: #1a6b2f;
		color: white;
		padding: 2.5rem 1rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	header h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
	}

	header p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin: 0;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	.page-links {
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.page-links a {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		color: #fff;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.page-links a:hover,
	.page-links a:focus-visible {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	section {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		background: #f9f9f9;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border-left: 5px solid #1a6b2f;
	}

	h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: #1a6b2f;
	}

	ul {
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
	}

	li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
</style>
